    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305072</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_001Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>探したぞ！　&lt;Klarth&gt;！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Finally found you, &lt;Klarth&gt;! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305160</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>探したのはこっちだ、
まったく……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's my line, actually... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305248</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はぁはぁ……
突然、駆け出すから……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Haa--Haa-- That was...way too much to run at once... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305316</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んだよ、もう……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Seriously, jeez! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305384</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>君たちも来たか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So you guys are here too. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305576</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_006Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なるほど……
『虹輪』を消すために
精霊の力が必要、か……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I see...so to erase the Prism Ring you need
the power of the Summon Spirits... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305576</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_007Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だったら、
例えば精霊晶核（アトミスムコア）を
使う、とかかな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In that case, we can use the help of Atomism Cores. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305644</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんだ、それ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What do you mean? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305728</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_009Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>精霊の力の源になってる物質さ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You could say it's the source of the Summon Spirit's power. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305896</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>やっぱり、そいつしかないか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Just as I thought, so we've got no choice... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305896</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>この子たちに
『エレメンツポット』を
ひとつ分けてやってくれないか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Will you give these kids an Elements' Pot? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306004</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_012Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>お安い御用だ、親友の頼みとあらばな。
何でも言ってくれ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, that was way too easy! I shouldn't
waste my time with simple jobs like these! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306144</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_013Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おまえがまた
戻ってきてくれて
よかったよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Seriously, though, I'm glad to see you're back. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306144</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_014Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>また一緒に
研究できるな！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We should do some research together sometime! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306204</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Heh... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306292</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_016Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それじゃあ、
これ……君たちに……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well then, take this guys... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306352</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>サンキュ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thanks! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306456</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_018Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それを持って、
精霊から精霊晶核を
受け取ればいい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In its insides you can hold the Spirit's Atomism Cores. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306520</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>精霊かぁ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The Summon Spirit's... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306624</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_020Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あと、エレメンツポットは
壊れやすいから気をつけてね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Remember, the Elements' Pot is fragile, be careful with it. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306704</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、ああ、うん。
わかったよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Gotcha, we'll do that. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306768</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>イフリート！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Efreet!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306864</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>イフリート。
おまえの精霊晶核を分けてくれ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Efreet, please lend us your Atomism Core.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306928</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>承知した</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Acknowledged.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>307012</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おぉっ……！
これが精霊晶核！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Woah! Is this an Atomism Core!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>307092</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……&lt;Dio&gt;、はしゃぎすぎ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...You sure are quick to celebrate...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>307256</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よし、それじゃあ
&lt;Red&gt;ローンヴァレイ&lt;White&gt;に行くとしよう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All right, our next destination is Lone Valley.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>307256</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_028&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Red&gt;ユークリッド&lt;White&gt;の東側にある
風の強い谷だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's northeast from Euclid. The wind there is very strong.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>307352</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_029&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>風……
そこに風の精霊シルフが
いるんですね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wind...the wind Summon Spirit Sylph lies there, right? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>307468</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_030&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ。私も最後まで
君たちに付き合おう。
協力すると言ったからな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Correct, I'll assist you until this is done. We'll need
to prove our strength yet again. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>307556</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_031&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よし、
&lt;Red&gt;ローンヴァレイ&lt;White&gt;に出発だ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>OK! Let's go to Lone Valley!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>307664</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_032&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;、気をつけて。
転んでエレメンツポット
割っちゃうよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;, be careful! The Elements' Pot
will break if it falls! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>32</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>307752</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_033&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>全然だいじょーぶ。
気ぃつけてるって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No problem! Nothin' to worry about!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>307816</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_070_034&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んもう……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>*sigh*</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>34</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
